@NODE "Foreword" "Foreword"
@TOC "MAIN"
                              ·ForeWord·

    Hello dudes. I`m proud to welcome you in first issue of new scene
mag called 'ScreamSheet'. You can ask, why i decided to make it.
Reason is simple - i`ve lot of free time and  i often have nothing to
do so now i`ve something to work on it. This mag will be not a great
'lots of articles' mag like 'FatAgnus' or 'RAW'. Main target of SS is
to be fast. So i`ll make new issue every month. This is not important
how many articles i`ll have - more important are News, Adverts and
messages - they (i hope) should be main part of this magazine. The
second thing which is important is code of this mag. As you see there
is no code - reason is simple - i don`t want to make any group coder
busy and this code is sure. There should`t be any gurus etc. I hope
that you`ll enjoy this form and support me with group news, adverts,
messages and of course articles. I think that`s all today. So wait
patiently for next issue and don`t forget to support SS.

@ENDNODE

