                            ·How to write·

    Well there is no limitation of articles subjects but don`t think
that i`ll place all articles that i get in this mag. i`ll select only
few best works and rest will be discarded or placed in next issue. Try
to write with sense and about hot things. SS is so fast that party
report from previous month will be probably discarded (or if  enjoy
this report - placed in magazine). Next thing - try to write
interesting articles because i don`t want to lost any reader because
he was bored when he readed something in SS. Write articles in english
only, because i prefer to translate something from english to polish
than from polish to english. You don`t need to format text but if you
want - make it for 72 columns. i think that`s all but if  get any good
idea i`ll place her (idea) here :)

